comments: Eubanks (PHX) and Allen (CLE) briefly engage and disengage as they pursue the rebound.
Eubanks (PHX) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Cavaliers.
Allen (PHX) applies a stayed forearm to Garland's (CLE) side, and the contact at the end of the drive is marginal.
Garland (CLE) goes to, not through, Allen's (PHX) space as they come together at the same spot in the lane.
Durant (PHX) does not maintain legal guarding position and initiates contact with Porter Jr.'s (CLE) left arm which affects his driving shot attempt.
LeVert (CLE) brings his hand forward towards Durant's (PHX) front, and the contact during the drive is marginal.
Eubanks (PHX) makes contact with the ball, and with the part of Allen's (CLE) right hand that is on the ball, and deflects the ball away from Allen as they pursue the rebound.
Eubanks (PHX) cleanly dislodges the ball from Allen (CLE).  Any ensuing arm contact after the dislodge is considered incidental.
Eubanks (PHX) cleanly deflects the ball away from Allen (CLE), and the ensuing arm contact from Allen is incidental.
Booker (PHX) slides his hand across Okoro's (CLE) upper body, and marginal contact occurs as Okoro dribbles behind his back.
Replay review of the out of bounds called on Okoro (CLE) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Okoro's right foot is out of bounds when he receives the pass along the sideline.
LeVert (CLE) commits a take foul on Durant (PHX).
Porter Jr. (CLE) brings his hand forward and makes contact with Allen's (PHX) arm as he attempts to pass the ball.
Durant (PHX) rests a forearm alongside Garland's (CLE) side, and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Durant (PHX) cleanly dislodges the ball from Allen (CLE).
Okoro (CLE) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
